aima.core.search.framework

Interface SearchForStates

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AStarSearch, BestFirstSearch, BreadthFirstSearch, DepthFirstSearch, DepthLimitedSearch, GreedyBestFirstSearch, HillClimbingSearch, IterativeDeepeningSearch, PrioritySearch, SimulatedAnnealingSearch, UniformCostSearch

    public interface SearchForStates
    Interface for all AIMA3e search algorithms which forget the exploration history and return just a single state which is hopefully a goal state. This search framework expects all search algorithms to provide some metrics and to actually explore the search space by expanding nodes.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
